    <item>
      <title>法国公投后欧元上涨，中国股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-gains-on-french-voting-china-eyed-after-pmi-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元跟随欧洲股指期货上涨，因为市场猜测玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党将难以在法国大选中赢得绝对多数席位，这缓解了投资者对欧洲第二大经济体将采取更为激进的政策转变的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-gains-on-french-voting-china-eyed-after-pmi-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司将以 47 亿美元股票交易收购 Spirit Aero</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/boeing-agrees-to-buy-spirit-aero-for-4-7-billion-in-stock-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司同意以每股 37.25 美元的价格回购 Spirit AeroSystems Holdings Inc.，这是一项全股票交易，对该供应商的估值为 47 亿美元，结束了长达二十年的分离，目前这家陷入困境的美国飞机制造商正试图修复其制造缺陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/boeing-agrees-to-buy-spirit-aero-for-4-7-billion-in-stock-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:44:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
